gomodel:SYNGO_1035  a    owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment     "Rationale: Using an antibody raised against human presenilin-1 authors show the accumulation of presenilin immunoreactivity in the dendrite in membrane below the PSD. They comment on a more modest pre-synaptic staining.\n\n22/8/2017 Pim\n- Authors state: \"The immunoreactivity localized to tubulovesicular profiles (asterisks), which likely represent elements of the SER (PSD, postsynaptic density)\". Experimental description: Materials and methods: Rhesus monkeys (n=4).........." ;
        lego:modelstate  "production" ;
        dc:contributor   "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3185-5709" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0938-8534" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7351-8706" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0755-5899" ;
